headline: Culver's Launches Cereal Concrete Mixers Inspired by Classic Breakfast Favorites
summary: The nostalgic, comforting taste of milk at the bottom of a cereal bowl has inspired everything from coffee creamers to cocktails and even made its way into surprisingly savory courses in fine dining. Now, for a limited time only, Culver's guests will have the opportunity to experience beloved cereal brands combined with the smooth, creamy texture of Fresh Frozen Custard for a flavorful twist on a familiar favorite.
